genresAdvancedInfo.name: salsa cristiana
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Salsa cristiana is a unique fusion of salsa music and Christian lyrics. It combines the rhythms of salsa with uplifting and inspirational messages, making it a popular choice for religious gatherings and events. Salsa cristiana is often performed by Christian artists and bands, and its message of hope and faith resonates with audiences around the world.
